1. How to change the username and password for database login?
    a. Go to assets/Php/db_connection.php
    b. Change the username and password in the defining sentences of DB_NAME and DB_PPASS'.

2. How to deploy the app after making changes?
    a. Open the terminal.
    b. Navigate into the dashboard folder.
    c. Type "ng build --base-href=/iiot/" in the terminal, this command updates the 'dist' folder.
    d. Delete everything except .ftpquota nad .htaccess files from the server and upload everything in dist folder to the server
       
        Remove the cache from the browser and run the app.
    
